casebody.data:
Johnny DUPIGNEY
v.
COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided November 14, 2018

Megan L. Wade, assigned counsel, in support of the petition.

Kathryn W. Bare, assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The petitioner Johnny Dupigney's petition for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court, 183 Conn. App. 852, 193 A.3d 1274 (2018), is denied.

ROBINSON, C. J., did not participate in the consideration of or decision on this petition.
